quran[32]{c,v,t}:
  36,28,Kawom geuh teutap jipubuet salah 3 Di likot gopnyan hana peue le that Uleh Hadharat teuntra Neuyue krah Hana Neukirem dum malaikat Nėéuyue prang rakyat nyang pubuet salah
  36,29,Cukop ngon deumpek sigoe nyang that-that Bandum jih teupat nyawong meusiblah
  36,30,Sayang takalon nasib dum rakyat Rasul Hadharat jikheun beurakah Jiulok-ulok jikheun sulet that
  36,31,Hana jilihat nyang ka Neubalah Peue hana jieu padum le umat Sabab khianat dilee keu Allah Bandum binasa hana seulamat Hana woe meuhat bandum ka leupah
  36,32,Umat nyan bandum keudeh meusapat Ukeu Hadharat Neumeung bri balah
  36,33,Lom saboh tanda kuasa Neuh that Tuhan Hadharat kuasa leupah Tanoh nyang mate udep le siat Timoh le ligat kayee nyang ceudah Jimeuboh kayee rasa jih lazat Tapajoh ligat mangat sileupah
  36,34,Timoh di lampoh kurma ngon inab Babah han seungap tapajoh bagah Teupanca ngon krueng ie jeureuengeh that
  36,35,Tapajoh ligat peue nyang na mudah Pajoh boh kayee peugot bu lukat Chuko le ligat keu nikmat Allah Pakon di kaphe hana jiingat Hana meu siat chuko keu Allah
  36,36,Tuhanku sidroe Maha Suci that i Timoh lat-batat takalon indah Inong ngon agam meujudo meuhat Saban ngon rakyat dum hamba Allah Bandum meujudo han ek tatupat Tuhan Hadharat bandum Neuulah
  36,37,Teuma saboh treuk tanda raya that Kuasa meuhat sidroe Potallah Malam ngon uroe gantoe siat-at ‘Oh Iheuh trang that-that seupot sileupah
  36,38,Mata uroe jak sabe bak teumpat Hana meu siat meusireuk langkah Meunan Neukada uleh Hadharat Tuhan meugah that ‘eleumee luah
  36,39,Buleuen di langet phon-phon ubit that Teuma deuh bulat malam limong blah Dudoe meugisa ubit lom meuhat Sang mata sadeup hu meujeureulah
  36,40,Buleuen ngon uroe han tom meusapat Tuhan Hadharat sit Neupeusiblah 3 Han tom meureumpok bak saboh teumpat Na jalan teupat meusiblah-siblah
  36,41,Saboh tanda treuk teuga Hadharat Kapai nyang sarat lam laot luah Aneuk ngon cuco soe meu neurangkat Lam kapai ligat jitamong bagah
  36,42,Laen nibak nyan keundraan di darat Han ek tahisab macam le leupah
  36,43,Meunyo Neukheundak uleh Hadharat Kapai nyan siat anco ngon bicah Ureueng dum karam tulong han sapat
  36,44,Meu kon Hadharat hana soe peuglah Meulengkan meu na Kamoe bri rahmat Seulamat siat han mate bagah
  36,45,‘Oh Rasul peugah ubak dum umat Beuthat taingat kuasa Allah Kawom nyang dilee hana seulamat Dudoe pih meuhat hana meuubah Bandum atranyoe meu tatem ingat Keu gata rahmat Neubri le Allah
  36,46,Sayang takalon teuma dum umat ‘Oh teuka ayat tron nibak Allah Muka ho laen jipaleng ligat
  36,47,Lom geupeuingat teuma geupeugah Raseukiteuh le Tuhan bri meuhat Ureueng meularat tabri seudeukah Teuma jijaweub le kaphe sisat k Jikheun bak umat iman keu Allah Ureueng nyan meunan kada Hadharat Hana meuhajat di jih napakah Meunyoe Neumeu jok uleh Hadharat Kon Neubri ligat peue nyang jeut susah Keubit nyoe gata nyata that sisat
  36,48,Jikheun lom meuhat kaphe seurakah Janjiteuh nyang nyoe pajan taintat Meunyoe beuna that gata tapeugah
  36,49,Hana peue jipreh hukom Hadharat Sit troh le siat kon trep sileupah Sigo geudeumpek le malaikat Abeh dum teupat teungeh meubantah
  36,50,Hana meuteumee wasiet meusiat Sabab Hadharat ka Neupeurintah Hana le jiwoe ubak keurabat Tinggai dum meuhat hana peue peugah
  36,51,Geuyup beuragoe le malaikat f Bandum jih meuhat beudoh le bagah Bandum geubangket ngon badan bulat Geuyue meuhadap keudeh bak Allah
  36,52,Watee nyan jikheun le kaphe sisat Ceulaka that-that tanyoe sileupah Soe nyang peubangket tanyoe bak teumpat Teuntee Hadharat nyang Maha Murah Janji uroejeh ka teuka meuhat Rasul beuna that ban nyang geupeugah
  36,53,Sigo geudeumpek le malaikat Bandum meusapat keudeh bak Allah
  36,54,Uroe nyoe nyata Tuhan ade that Ban laku adat bandum Neubalah Hana elanya meu sidroe rakyat Amai dum meuhat keudroe jipeugah
  36,55,Asoe churuga jinoe seunang that Geuduek ngon sahbat meupeugah-peugah
  36,56,Budiyadari sajan meusapat Ngon judo meuhat bineh peuratah Di yup bak kayee nyang reului that-that Meusadeu ligat seunang sileupah
  36,57,Pajoh boh kayee nyang lazat-lazat Lom peue nyang hajat cit troh le bagah
  36,58,Seulamat datang Neukheun le ligat Uleh Hadharat nyang Maha Murah
  36,59,Teuma di kaphe suroh Hadharat Beumeukleh teumpat uroenyoe di kah